children.Text: Slider has been extracted from react-native core and will be removed in a future release. It can now be installed and imported from '@react-native-community/slider' instead of 'react-native'. See https://github.com/react-native-community/react-native-slider

Picker has been extracted from react-native core and will be removed in a future release. It can now be installed and imported from '@react-native-community/picker' instead of 'react-native'. See https://github.com/react-native-community/react-native-picker

AsyncStorage has been extracted from react-native core and will be removed in a future release. It can now be installed and imported from '@react-native-community/async-storage' instead of 'react-native'. See https://github.com/react-native-community/async-storage
